title: PM Modi-led NDA‚Äôs show of strength as Droupadi Murmu files nomination for President post
description: It was a massive show of strength by the NDA today as Droupadi Murmu filed her nomination papers in the Parliament for the post of next President of India with PM Narendra Modi by her side. PM Modi had proposed her name for the nomination, which was seconded by Defence Minister Rajnath Singh. She was accompanied by a host of NDA leaders to the parliament, including BJP President JP Nadda, Home Minister Amit Shah, Defence Minister Rajnath Singh, chief ministers of BJP-ruled states. Leaders of YSR Congress and Biju Janata Dal - both non-NDA parties - were also in Parliament to back her nomination. Droupadi Murmu, the first woman tribal leader to file her nomination for the top constitutional post of the country, will face opposition candidate Yashwant Sinha. The presidential election would be held on July 18 and the result would be out on July 21. Watch this video for more information.|#droupadimurmu #president #narendramodi #nda #pmmodi #rajnathsingh #amitshah #jpnadda #bjp #yogiadityanath #presidentialelection2022 #presidentialrace #yashwantsinha

title: Tampang Indra Kenz Tiba di Kejari Tangsel Beserta 2 Mobil Mewahnya
description: TANGERANG, KOMPAS.TV  Tersangka kasus penipuan dan investasi bodong Indra Kenz tiba di Kejaksaan Negeri, Kota Tangerang Selatan, Serpong, Jumat (24/6/2022).||||Tersangka diserahkan setelah berkasnya dinyatakan lengkap.||||Indra pun datang lebih awal dari jadwal yang sudah diinformasikan kepada awak media.||||Baca Juga Diduga Terima Rp 9 M dan Sembunyikan Aset Kripto Rp 35 M, Adik Indra Kenz Ditangkap Bareskrim Polri! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282477/diduga-terima-rp-9-m-dan-sembunyikan-aset-kripto-rp-35-m-adik-indra-kenz-ditangkap-bareskrim-polri||||Penyidik juga menyerahkan dua unit mobil mewah bermerek Tesla berpelat B 14 DRA dan Ferrari California dengan pelat B 8877 HP, Sebagai barang bukti.||||Rencananya indra kenz akan ditahan di Kejaksaan Negeri Tangerang Selatan, selama menunggu sidang perdananya digelar di Pengadilan Negeri Kota Tangerang.||||Dalam kasus ini polisi juga menetapkan adik Indra Kenz Nathania Kesuma; mitra aplikasi Binomo Indra Kenz dan Fakar Suhartami Pratama atau Fakarich; admin Indra Kenz Wiky Mandara Nurhalim jadi tersangka. ||||Video Editor: Arief|| |||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/302408/tampang-indra-kenz-tiba-di-kejari-tangsel-beserta-2-mobil-mewahnya

title: ‚ÄòAmerican right to‚Ä¶‚Äô: Biden denounces SC ruling as U.S. Senate passes gun control bill
description: For the first time in nearly 30 years, the U.S. senate approved a bipartisan gun violence bill, clearing the way for final congressional approval. The vote on final passage of the gun violence bill was 65-33. The Bipartisan Safer Communities Act, which was backed by all 50 Democratic senators and 15 Republicans, includes tougher background checks for the youngest gun buyers, keeping firearms from more domestic violence offenders and help states put in place red flag laws that make it easier for authorities to take weapons from people adjudged dangerous. It would also fund local programs for school safety, mental health and violence prevention. Meanwhile, the U.S. Supreme Court ruled that Americans have a fundamental right to carry a handgun in public. The 6-3 decision strikes down a more than century-old New York law that required a person to prove they had a legitimate self-defense need to receive a permit to carry a handgun outside the home. title: Modi govt picks Dinkar Gupta, who was shunted by Cong as Punjab DGP, for NIA top job
description: The govt has appointed former Punjab DGP Dinkar Gupta as the Director General of the National Investigation Agency (NIA). Dinkar Gupta, 1987-batch Indian Police Service (IPS) officer of Punjab cadre, will serve as NIA boss till March 31, 2024. Gupta will take over from CRPF DG Kuldiep Singh, who was given additional charge of NIA chief in May last year. Gupta was removed as Punjab police chief by Cong-led Channi govt in October last year. title: Doomsday Movie Review/Summary In Hindi/Urdu
description: Credits |Production companies|Rogue Pictures|Crystal Sky Pictures|Intrepid Pictures|Scion Films|Distributed by|Universal Pictures (International)|Concorde Filmverleih (Germany)|Ster-Kinekor (South Africa)|Directed by|Neil Marshall|Written by|Neil Marshall|Produced by|Benedict Carver|Steven Paul|Starring|Rhona Mitra|Bob Hoskins|Adrian Lester|David O'Hara|Malcolm McDowell|Cinematography|Sam McCurdy|Edited by|Andrew MacRitchie|Music by|Tyler Bates|Synopsis |In 2008, a killer virus, known as the "Reaper virus", has infected the country of Scotland, causing its entire population to become hysterical and homicidally insane. Unable to contain the outbreak or cure the infected, the British government builds a massive 30-foot wall that isolated Scotland from the rest of Great Britain. Whilst the quarantine was deemed a success, the extreme method employed by the government destroys diplomatic and economic relations between the UK and the rest of the world, turning the state itself into a pariah state. This led to massive unemployment, civil unrest and extreme economic turmoil, causing the UK to collapse into a dystopia.|In 2035, 27 years after the start of the quarantine, a group of armed police officers discover several people in London infected with Reaper virus during a routine investigation. Prime Minister John Hatcher shares satellite footage of survivors in Scotland with domestic security chief Captain Nelson. Believing a cure may exist, Hatcher orders Nelson to send a team into Scotland to find medical researcher Dr. Kane who was working on a cure when Scotland was quarantined. Nelson chooses his top police officer, Major Eden Sinclair, to lead the team. According to Nelson, Sinclair also hails from Scotland, where she escaped from when the quarantine began at the cost of her right eye. For Sinclair the mission is also personal, as she hopes to learn if her mother survived or not.|After leaving the train, Sinclair's group is spotted and kidnapped by soldiers armed with archaic weapons and armour. They are taken to a medieval castle and imprisoned. Their leader, who is really Marcus Kane, tells Sinclair the truth: there is no cure‚Äîonly people with a natural immunity, which was the reason why Scotland was placed under quarantine. Originally a medical researcher, he was devastated when his family was left behind during the quarantine. After losing his wife, Kane became a twisted, sadistic lord who now hides from the world around him. In conclusion, Kane places blame on science for the downfall of not only the government in Scotland, but civilization of the country itself. As an example of his vengeance against science, Kane sentences her and her group to death, pitting Sinclair against Telamon, his executioner, in a small fighting ground to entertain his followers. During the duel, Sinclair subdues and kills Telamon while the rest of the group escapes, retrieving their equipment and rescuing Sinclair.|Cally and Stirling board the gunship with Canaris while Sinclair returns to her old house in search of her mother, followed by Nelson, who flew into the quarantine zone to speak with her. While Sinclair learns that her mother perished in despair during the quarantine, she is able to retrieve a picture of her. Sinclair gives Nelson a recording of Canaris' genocidal coup d'√©tat scheme, the evidence that would save the UK from extinction once and for all. The recording is later broadcast to the rest of the country, much to Canaris' dismay, as it spells doom to his career and subsequential criminal conviction.|Meanwhile, Sinclair retrieves Sol's head and returns it to his gang; she throws the head onto the ground, announcing to the marauders, ‚ÄúIf you're hungry, try a piece of your friend‚Äù. The marauders stand in shock for a moment of stunned silence before bursting into cheering, accepting Sinclair as their new leader.

title: WATCH: Rep. Adam Kinzinger‚Äôs closing statement on Day 5 of hearings | Jan. 6 hearings
description: Adam Kinzinger, R-Ill., gave a closing statement on June 23 as the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack presented its findings to the public.|Former top Justice Department officials provided roughly two hours of testimony, detailing how they questioned and pushed back on former President Donald Trump‚Äôs pressure campaign to change the outcome of the 2020 election. They threatened to resign en masse if the former president decided to overhaul the department‚Äôs leadership by appointing another DOJ official Jeffrey Clark, who was willing to cast doubt on the legitimacy of the election results without evidence.|‚ÄúPresident Trump tried to erase his loss at the ballot box by parachuting an unqualified man into the top job at justice. It was a power play to win at all costs, with no regard for the will of the American people. It was about ignoring millions of votes,‚Äù Kinzinger said.|Kinzinger said the country owed ‚Äúa great debt of gratitude‚Äù to the DOJ officials who refused Trump‚Äôs demands.|‚ÄúReal leaders who stood for justice when it was in grave peril. Who put their country first when the leader of the free world demanded otherwise. They threatened to resign rather than corrupt our democracy and thanks largely to each of them, President Trump's coup failed.‚Äù|The hearing, the fifth of several planned by the Jan. 6 committee, focused on Trump‚Äôs pressure  on the Department of Justice to overturn the 2020 presidential election results. title: Rory McIlroy shoots 8-under 62 | Round 1 | Travelers | 2022
description: In the opening round of the 2022 Travelers Championship, Rory McIlroy carded an 8-under 62, one clear of the field for a tie for the lead with J.T. Poston heading into Friday.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Fresh off a second-place finish at the 2022 U.S. Open, World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler leads the field this week at TPC River Highlands, while 2021 winner Harris English will look to defend his title in his third start since having hip surgery in February. However, with the top three players in the FedExCup Standings also in action, the Georgian will face stiff competition. These include Rory McIlroy, who will be full of confidence after defending his title at the RBC Canadian Open and subsequently finishing an impressive T5 at the U.S. Open. Sam Burns will be looking to continue his remarkable form, which has already seen him win three times on the PGA TOUR this season at the Sanderson Farms Championship, the Valspar Championship and the Charles Schwab Challenge. Other notable names to keep an eye on include FedExCup champion Patrick Cantlay, Jordan Spieth and Tommy Fleetwood. ||||Check out https://www.pgatour.com for complete coverage along with all the latest news, scoring, and stats!||||Follow PGA TOUR online:||Instagram: https://instagram.com/pgatour/  ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PGATour  ||Twitter: https://twitter.com/PGATOUR||TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@pgatour||SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/pgatour||||Sign up for exclusive coverage - http://www.pgatourlive.com||PGA TOUR Superstore - http://www.pgatoursuperstore.com/

title: WATCH: Former top DOJ official Donoghue on Jeffrey Clark's push on false election fraud claims
description: Richard Donoghue, former acting deputy attorney general, testified on June 23 as the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack presented its findings to the public.|Donoghue described to the committee how he and acting Attorney General Jeffrey Rosen tried to dissuade fellow DOJ official Jeffrey Clark from acting on claims of election fraud that were not supported by evidence. Clark had readied a letter meant for state legislatures in swing states that casted doubt on the 2020 election that had been won by President Joe Biden.|‚ÄúFor the department to insert into the political processes this way, I think, would have grave consequences for the country. It may very well spiral us into a constitutional crisis and I wanted to make sure he understood the gravity of the situation because he did not seem to appreciate it,‚Äù Donoghue recalled writing in a response to Clark.|Donoghue said Rosen was also ‚Äúexasperated‚Äù by Clark‚Äôs efforts and the three had a ‚Äúcontentious‚Äù meeting.|Despite the warning, Donoghue said Clark continued to investigate claims of election fraud, including an intelligence briefing that suggested foreign interference in the election, and argued for sending the letter.|‚ÄúWe thought perhaps once it was explained to him that there was no basis for that part of his concern, that he would retreat. But instead, he doubled down and said, ‚ÄòOK, there is no foreign interference. I still think there are enough allegations out there that we should go ahead and send this letter,‚Äô which shocked me even more than the initial one,‚Äù Donoghue said, ‚Äúbecause you would think after a couple of days of looking at this ‚Äì he, like we ‚Äì would have come to the same conclusion, that it was unfounded.‚Äù|The hearing, the fifth of several planned by the Jan. 6 committee, focused on Trump‚Äôs pressure  on the Department of Justice to overturn the 2020 presidential election results. In the year since its creation, the committee has conducted more than 1,000 interviews, seeking critical information and documents from people witness to, or involved in, the violence that day.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG  |Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour  |Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6  |Follow us: |TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@pbsnews  |Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour  |Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour |Subscribe: |PBS NewsHour podcasts: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/podcasts|Newsletters: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/subscribe

description: Richard Donoghue, former acting deputy attorney general, testified on June 23 as the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack presented its findings to the public.|Donoghue recounted an early January 2021 meeting with former President Donald Trump who asked whether he could replace acting Attorney General Jeffrey Rosen with lawyer Jeffrey Clark who ‚Äì unlike other DOJ officials ‚Äì was willing to pursue false allegations of election fraud.|‚ÄúAt some point, the conversation turned to whether Jeff Clark was even qualified, competent to run the Justice Department. Which in my mind, he clearly was not. And it was a heated conversation,‚Äù Donoghue told the committee.|‚ÄúI thought it was useful to point out to the president that Jeff Clark simply didn't have the skills, the ability and the experience to run the department.‚Äù|Donoghue added that it was ‚Äúabsurd‚Äù to believe that Clark could get the department to pursue allegations of election fraud without the skills to lead the organization.|‚ÄúHe's telling you that he's going to take charge of the department of 115,000 employees, including the entire FBI, and turn the place on a dime and conduct nationwide criminal investigations that will produce results in a matter of days. It's impossible. It's absurd. It's not going to happen, and it's going to fail,‚Äù he added.|The hearing, the fifth of several planned by the Jan. 6 committee, focused on Trump‚Äôs pressure  on the Department of Justice to overturn the 2020 presidential election results. description: Start building your ideal daily routine  The first 100 people who click on the link will get 25% OFF  Fabulous Premium https://thefab.co/screencrush|Ms. Marvel episode 3 gives us some answers about Kamala‚Äôs bangle‚Ä¶but a lot more questions about where she came from, and how this connects to the Kree, and to Shang-Chi and the Legend of the TenRings. We explained the connection to the Marvel Cinematic Universe and how this show is setting up the next big crossover event, The Young Avengers.|If you're new, Subscribe! ‚Üí http://bit.ly/subscribe-screencrush|Go here ‚Üí http://screencrush.com/|Like us ‚Üí https://www.facebook.com/ScreenCrush|Follow us ‚Üí https://twitter.com/screencrushnews|Get our newsletter ‚Üí http://screencrush.com/newsletter/|Written and Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)|Written by Srinidhi Rao (http://instagram.com/shishurao)|Edited by Harriet Lengel-Enright, Sean martin, and Ethan Lavinsky|This episode finally gives us our villain, draws battle lines, and a kind of origin for the powers. But I‚Äôve got a theory about the Bangle and the Jinn, where they come from, and how this ties in to Shang Chi and the legend of the ten rings that I‚Äôm going to go over a little later in the video. |We opened in British occupied INdia in 1942. This is 5 years before INdia and Pakistan gained independence,and also 5 years before the Partition that we‚Äôve heard about in past episodes [bad time, etc.].|This is significant because it gives us a clue about what happened to Kamala‚Äôs grandmother Aisha after she leaves Nadya here. Later on Nadya says [those who betray me], so she thinks that amala‚Äôs grandmother was a traitor. I think this is because Aisha met a humble earthman, fell in love, and did not want to return to her home dimension. |But first let‚Äôs talk about this juicy scene and all the easter eggs. So the Jinn are looking for two bangles. I mentioned this last week, but it could be that the bangles are the MCI version of the nega bands. |These bands were worn by the original Captain Marvel, and‚Ä¶basically they connected him to another dimension called the negative zone, where he and a guy named Rick Jones would take turns being trapped. They also gave his powers, and were powerful relics from the Kree empire.|You remember the Kree, from Guardians, Agents of Shield, Captain marvel. The kree have bene visiting earth for thousands of years‚Äìin fact peggy carter takes a kree body from the nazis in agents of sheild. Now the arm here is blue, like the Kree which would support the theory that this is a Kree body. And that the bangle is a Kree relic.|But I‚Äôve got another theory about who this could be that I‚Äôll go over later in the video. |Then Nadya gives us a few answers about who they are. She says they were from another dimension, and were exiled. Now the episode gives us a pretty great explanation of the jinn [her dad, genie, etc.]  They are a certain kind of spirit in Islam, similar to an ange;l, that can take the form of an animal or a human. |And actually, the jinn were first mentioned here in episode 1 [clip, amir making fun of her]. And she also gives other names they have been called. For instance, the Unseen. There was a group of aliens called the unseen in Marvel comics in the 1950s, and they attacked all the capitalist countries of the world. This was also a code name Nick Fury adopted for a while. |Now she also says they call themselves the clandestine. In the comics, in the 1990s, this is a group of supervillains. So you could say this is a version of that team. In fact, one of the members was a jinn. Here they're all Jinns from another reality. |And they reveal the source of their powers, the Noor. This is a common Arabic word meaning light, but they spin this into a new concept, as energy forms another dimension. |None of them were able to use the bangle, but Kamala could. And this is a metaphor for the experience of the American immigrant. Later in the episode, her mother talks about how hard it was when they moved to America [clip]. |Her mother never truly fit into western, american culture. But her daughter, Kamala can. So, just like the Jinn need someone who is half from earth to return home, Kamal‚Äôs parents need a daughter from America to help them feel at home. |This series is rooted in themes of family and community, whether they be friendships, family, religion‚Äìor your inter dimensional cousins who want to eat your brain, or whatever. |She also hints that someday Kamaran‚Äôs abilities will manifest [clip]. And in the comics, his superpower is bioluminescence‚Äìso here it looks like the noor-the light, will be his power as well. |And by the way, this guy is watching Zoe‚Äôs popcorn video that we heard about form damage control [clip]. |#MsMarvel #EasterEggs #shangchi

title: Maverick City Music: Tiny Desk Concert
description: This year, NPR Music is celebrating Black Music Month with an array of brand new Tiny Desk concerts ‚Äî both from home and from behind our beloved Desk. Together, these artists represent the past, present and future of Black music. This month of carefully curated shows is a celebration of Black artists expressing themselves in ways we've never seen before, and of the Tiny Desk's unique way of showcasing that talent.|Suraya Mohamed | June 23, 2022|Almost 30 musicians, choir members and staff of the contemporary worship music collective Maverick City Music entered the NPR lobby and crowded the security desk to undergo COVID protocols. Even through the dull process of checking vaccination cards and test results, there was a real feeling of excitement for what was about to happen.|Some of the choir members were eager not only for the upcoming Tiny Desk concert but for later that evening, when they were scheduled to perform at a sold-out 20,000-seat arena nearby. A few of them had only previously performed with Maverick City Music in small venues and couldn't wait to move from the Tiny Desk to a big stage. Once upstairs, the group's enthusiasm grew during the set up and sound check. Even the NPR production staff was buzzing because we had not recorded such a large ensemble in our office in more than two years.|Once the performance started, Maverick City Music did what it always does. The members of the group became one voice, sharing beautiful music and spreading the good word with messages of hope, change and love. The group describes itself as a megaphone for a community of creatives that has been pushed to the margins of the industry of church music. title: Adam Savage's One Day Builds: Chinatown Stunt Knife (Corridor Crew FX Challenge!)
description: In this very SPECIAL One Day Build,  a collaboration with @Corridor Crew,  Adam replicates one of his favorite practical effects: the bloody knife-attack scene from the 1974 film Chinatown. title: Praktik SPBU Nakal, Kepergok Kurangi Takaran BBM dan Raup Keuntungan Hingga Rp 7 Miliar!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Anda pernah mengisi penuh BBM kendaraan anda, tapi merasa BBM cepat habis atau volumenya tidak sesuai dengan harga yang dibayar???||||Bisa jadi anda menjadi korban praktik curang SPBU nakal.||||Seperti yang dilakukan SPBU di Jalan Raya Serang-Jakarta, Kilometer 70 ini, Manajer dan Pengelola SPBU ini ketahuan mengurangi takaran BBM.||||Direktorat Reserse Kriminal Khusus Polda Banten mendapati pemilik dan Manajer SPBU melakukan modifikasi pada dispenser SPBU dengan remote control atau perangkat pengendali jarak jauh.||||Praktik curang SPBU ini dilakukan dengan mengurangi takaran BBM  sebanyak 0,5-1 liter per 20 liter pengisian.||||Baca Juga Megawati Belum Deklarasikan Nama Capres yang Akan Diusung: Masih Disimpan! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/302254/megawati-belum-deklarasikan-nama-capres-yang-akan-diusung-masih-disimpan||||Praktik curang ini merugikan konsumen yang mengisi BBM per harinya, mulai Rp 4 juta hingga Rp 6 juta.||||Praktik curang SPBU ini dilakukan sejak tahun 2016, selama kurang lebih 6 tahun SPBU nakal ini meraup keuntungan dari kecurangan sebesar Rp 7 miliar.||||Polisi akhirnya menetapkan 2 orang pengelola SPBU sebagai tersangka.||||Atas perbuatannya, keduanya dijerat dengan pasal berlapis dari Undang-Undang Perlindungan Konsumen dan Undang-Undang tentang Metrologi Legal.||||Namun polisi memutuskan untuk tidak menahan kedua tersangka dengan alasan faktor usia dan kesehatan.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/302273/praktik-spbu-nakal-kepergok-kurangi-takaran-bbm-dan-raup-keuntungan-hingga-rp-7-miliar

title: Supreme Court Strikes Down N.Y. Gun Limit Law
description: A divided US Supreme Court struck down a New York law that required people to show a special need to carry a handgun in public, ruling for the first time that the Second Amendment protects gun rights outside the home. President Joe Biden called on states to keep passing "commonsense" gun laws. It's the court's biggest gun-rights decision in more than a decade. Bloomberg's Greg Stohr is on "Balance of Power."

title: Lithuania 'ready' for Moscow RETALIATION over EU blockade of Kaliningrad
description: Lithuania is 'prepared' if Russia disconnects it from the regional power grid in retaliation for blocking rail shipments of some Russian goods to Moscow's Kaliningrad exclave the president said on Wednesday.|He spoke after the Kremlin warned Lithuania on Tuesday, that Moscow would respond to the ban on the transit of goods sanctioned by the EU to Kaliningrad in such a way that citizens of the Baltic state would feel the pain.|With relations between Moscow and the West at a half-century low over Russia's invasion of Ukraine, Lithuania banned the transit of goods sanctioned by the European Union across its territory to and from Kaliningrad, citing EU sanction rules.|Kaliningrad is sandwiched between NATO members Poland and Lithuania and supplied by rail via the territory of Lithuania.|Lithuania shut the route for transport of steel and other ferrous metals from mainland Russia on Saturday (June 18) saying it had to do so under EU sanctions that took effect that day.|"We are ready and we are prepared for unfriendly actions from Russia (in response), such as disconnection from the BRELL (power grid) system, or others," Lithuanian President Gitanas Nauseda said.|Thirty years after seceding from the then-Soviet Union and 17 years since joining the EU, Baltic states Lithuania, Latvia and Estonia still depend on Russia for stable power supplies.|However, Lithuania installed equipment on its power link to Poland last year to connect with the continental European grid quickly as an insurance policy in case Russia cuts off the flow of electricity, potentially causing blackouts.|Nauseda said Lithuania's status as a member of NATO meant Russia would not "challenge us in military sense".|He also said Lithuania will be expanding the list of goods it bars from reaching Kaliningrad, as phase-in periods for the EU sanctions are reached.|If the European Commission explained the content of sanctions to Russia "it could remove some of the current tensions" he added.|The Sun newspaper brings you the latest breaking news videos and explainers from the UK and around the world|Become a Sun Subscriber and hit the bell to be the first to know|Read title: Why Navy Sailors Train Inside A Tear Gas Chamber In Boot Camp | Boot Camp | Business Insider
description: We got an inside look at how US Navy recruits are exposed to tear gas during basic training. Insider spent five days at Navy Recruit Training Command, Great Lakes, where we observed recruits at various stages of their 10-week boot camp. During the fourth week of training, recruits learn how to properly don an M50 gas mask and are exposed to CS gas in the "confidence chamber." While wearing a gas mask, the recruits watch as an instructor burns a CS capsule over a hot plate, filling the chamber with gas. title: Megawati Bersyukur Jokowi Jadi Presiden Indonesia: Kok Bisa ya, Tahan Banting Banget!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Setelah 2 hari menggelar kegiatan, PDI Perjuangan Kamis (23/6/2022) ini menutup Rapat Kerja Nasional.||||Selama 2 hari Rapat Kerja Nasional, PDI Perjuangan membahas sejumlah agenda politik untuk Pemilihan Umum 2024.||||Termasuk koalisi dan siapa calon presiden yang diusung pada 2024.||||Megawati merasa bersyukur memiliki Presiden Jokowi sebagai pemimpin negara besar, Indonesia ini.||||"Saya juga heran loh, saya sampai tanya, padahal kurus ya, tapi kok bisa sih tahan banting banget," ucap Megawati.||||Megawati mengatakan akibat pengalaman hidupnya, ia bisa melihat orang dari sosok yang lebih dalam dan melihat potensi seseorang ke depannya.||||Baca Juga Ring 1 Jenderal TNI Dudung, Saya tidah pernah bermimpi menjadi KSAD | Cerita Militer di https://www.kompas.tv/article/302206/ring-1-jenderal-tni-dudung-saya-tidah-pernah-bermimpi-menjadi-ksad-cerita-militer||||Dalam pidato di penutupan Rakernas PDI-P, Megawati menyampaikan bahwa ia mencari pemimpin dengan melihat tantangan ke depan yang tidak ringan.||||Seperti yang telah dikatakan Presiden Jokowi saat pembukaan Rakernas, bahwa Jokowi merasa prihatin terkait tantangan yang dihadapi Indonesia ke depannya seperti ketidakpastian global, ancama resesi dunia, krisis pangan dan masih banyak lainnya.||||Maka dari itu, Megawati menginginkan dan mencari pemimpin yang tidak hanya mengandalkan elektoral semata.||||Pemimpin yang didambakan oleh rakyat adalah sosok yang kuat secara ideologis, sosok yang mumpuni, memiliki kemampuan memimpin tata kelola pemerintahan untuk negara Indonesia yang besar.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/302210/megawati-bersyukur-jokowi-jadi-presiden-indonesia-kok-bisa-ya-tahan-banting-banget

title: "You Merge With BJP, We Will Rebuild Sena": Sanjay Raut To Rebels
description: Maharashtra Chief Minister Uddhav Thackeray's loyalist and Shiv Sena MP Sanjay Raut on Thursday challenged the party's rebel camp led by Eknath Shinde to a floor test in the assembly, while also telling them that their chance to return to the party is still not lost. On the rebels' demand that Shiv Sena should break up with the NCP and Congress to ally with the BJP and form a new government, he said, "You (the rebels) should merge with the BJP. Shiv Sena remains our party."¬† Speaking to NDTV, Mr Raut responded to the Shinde camp's allegations that the chief minister's house 'Varsha' remained out of bounds for party legislators, "These are just excuses. title: In Japan, a real-life phoenix rises from the ashes of extinction
description: Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: |https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube|The toki, a Japanese crested ibis, used to soar above the rice paddies of Japan‚Äôs Sado Island, feasting on small frogs and insects. But by 1981, the bird was nearly extinct after being decimated by overhunting and the use of pesticides. In 2003, the last wild-born toki in Japan died of old age. Now, nearly 20 years later, an estimated 480 toki have returned to Sado, saved by a rare success story in a world where one in eight birds globally are facing extinction.|Support us:|https://subscribe.scmp.com|Follow us on:|Website:  https://www.scmp.com|Facebook:  https://facebook.com/scmp|Twitter:  https://twitter.com/scmpnews|Instagram:  https://instagram.com/scmpnews|Linkedin:  https://www.linkedin.com/company/south-china-morning-post/|#scmp #Environment #endangeredanimals

title: What do we know about the situation in Lysychansk? | Ukraine Update
description: President Volodymyr Zelenskyy has renewed his call for faster arms shipments to his country. Russian troops are intensifying their assault in the Donbas region. He described the situation there in his nightly address.|They are closing in on the city of Lysychansk, in eastern Donbas. Russian troops are now less than three kilometres from the city limits. They've already captured almost all the neighboring city of Severodonetsk. |Russian forces have also resumed pounding Ukraine's second-biggest city, Kharkiv, located near the Russian border. title: [Full] Ganjar Pranowo Bacakan Rekomendasi Rakernas II PDIP: Capres 2024 Hak Prerogatif Megawati
description: Toyota hadirkan T Intouch, teknologi yang dapat menghubungkan mobil dengan pemiliknya secara digital melalui aplikasi mToyota.https://bit.ly/3tUcpdI||||JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo sekaligus kader PDIP membacakan hasil rekomendasi Rakernas II PDIP.||||Rekomendasi Rakernas II PDIP ini dibacakan oleh Ganjar Pranowo pada Kamis, 23 Juni 2022.||||Adapun sejumlah rekomendasi dari Rakernas II PDIP adalah menegaskan pentingnya pembumian Pancasila. Pancasila sebagai ideology landasan dan penuntun strategis pemerintahan. Kurikulum pembelajaran harus memuat Pancasila sebagai mata pelajaran wajib.||||Baca Juga Bahas Penanganan Covid-19 hingga Pemilihan Capres 2024, Ganjar Pranowo Bacakan Hasil Rakernas PDI-P! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/302110/bahas-penanganan-covid-19-hingga-pemilihan-capres-2024-ganjar-pranowo-bacakan-hasil-rakernas-pdi-p||||Rekomendasi Rakernas II PDIP selanjutnya adalah mendukung sepenuhnya pemerintah mempercepat pemulihan dampak Covid-19.||||Serta menyerahkan pemilihan Capres 2024 dari PDIP sebagai hak prerogatif dari Ketum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/302113/full-ganjar-pranowo-bacakan-rekomendasi-rakernas-ii-pdip-capres-2024-hak-prerogatif-megawati

title: Yenny Wahid Sebut PKB Gus Dur, Cak Imin Beri Balasan: Ngapain Ikut Ikut Ngatur?
description: Toyota hadirkan T Intouch, teknologi yang dapat menghubungkan mobil dengan pemiliknya secara digital melalui aplikasi mToyota.https://bit.ly/3tUcpdI||||JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Putri Presiden ke-4 RI Abdurrahman Wahid atau Gus Dur Yenny Wahid menyebut dirinya bukanlah bagian dari Partai Kebangkitan Bangsa (PKB) di bawah Muhaimin Iskandar atau Cak Imin.||||Ia juga menyebut bahwa dirinya adalah bagian dari PKB asuhan sang ayah, Gus Dur.||||Komentar tersebut ia sampaikan setelah hadir menjadi pembicara di Kampus IPDN, Jatinangor, Kamis (23/6).||||Baca Juga Yenny Wahid Menjawab Dirinya PKB Gus Dur, Bukan PKB Cak Imin: Memang Begitu di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301941/yenny-wahid-menjawab-dirinya-pkb-gus-dur-bukan-pkb-cak-imin-memang-begitu||||"Saya enggak tahu karena udah bukan bagian PKB saat ini. Saya PKB Gus Dur, bukan PKB Cak Imin," ujar Yenny pada wartawan.||||"Kalau surveinya enggak terlalu ngangkat, enggak usah terlalu ngotot," ucap Yenny.||||Sesaat setelah komentar tersebut menjadi pebincangan, Cak Imin beri tanggapan melalui media sosial.||||Lewat akun Twitter @cakiminNOW, ia meminta Yenny untuk tidak ikut atur-atur PKB.||||Cak Imin juga minta Yenny mengurus partai besutannya yang dianggap gagal lolos dalam Pemilu.||||"Yeni itu bukan PKB, bikin partai sendiri saja gagal lolos. Beberapa kali Pemilu nyerang PKB enggak ngaruh, PKB malah naik terus suaranya, jadi ngapain ikut-ikut ngatur PKB?," tulis Cak Imin.||||"Hidupin saja partaimu yang gagal itu. PKB sudah nyaman kok" tutupnya.||||Cak Imin dan PKB kini resmi berkoalisi dengan Partai Gerindra asuhan Prabowo Subianto untuk menyambut Pilpres 2024.||||Video Editor: Firmansyah||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301964/yenny-wahid-sebut-pkb-gus-dur-cak-imin-beri-balasan-ngapain-ikut-ikut-ngatur

title: L'ultimo addio alla piccola Elena, ai funerali la folla prega e grida 'vergogna'
description: Un lunghissimo applauso ha accompagnato in piazza Duomo a Catania l'arrivo della bara bianca della piccola Elena Del Pozzo, la bambina di non ancora cinque anni uccisa dalla madre Martina Patti. In cielo si sono alzati palloncini bianchi a forma di cuore. All'interno della Cattedrale l'arcivescovo, Monsignor Luigi Renna, ha puntato l'attenzione sul dramma che vivono i bambini a causa dei conflitti dei genitori. Al termine della celebrazione la stessa folla che pregava ha urlato 'vergogna, vergogna', riferendosi alla madre. Tra gli oggetti cari alla piccola, il nonno paterno di Elena ha poggiato sulla bara bianca un palloncino di Bing. .¬† .Video di Alessandro Puglia

title: Warganet Indonesia Serbu Akun Instagram Mahathir Mohamad seusai Klaim Kepulauan Riau Milik Malaysia
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Pernyataan mantan Perdana Menteri (PM) Malaysia Mahathir Mohamad memancing kemarahan warganet Indonesia.|Pasalnya, Mahathir mengklaim bahwa Kepulauan Riau adalah bagian dari Tanah Melayu Malaysia.|Hal ini langsung membuat warganet Indonesia menyerbu akun Instagram Mahathir.|Beragam reaksi warganet Indonesia membanjiri kolom komentar di akun Instagram Mahathir.|Mereka menuliskan komentar berisi kecaman soal pernyataan eks PM Malaysia itu.|"Maksudnya apa pak mau claim kepulauan Riau?," tulis akun |rmayda_.|Banyak yang menilai ucapan Mahathir sebagai provokasi untuk memecah belah Indonesia dan Malaysia.|"apakah ini provokasi ngajak perang dari pihak sana," tulis akun samsul_arifin45.|Sebelumnya, pernyataan Mahathir disampaikan dalam sebuah forum yang digelar di Selangor, pada Minggu (19/6).|Mahathir mengatakan bahwa Malaysia seharusnya mengklaim Kepulauan Riau menjadi miliknya.|Tak hanya itu, ia juga menyebut bahwa Singapura merupakan bagian dari negaranya.|‚ÄúSeharusnya kita tidak hanya menuntut agar Pedra Branca atau Pulau Batu Puteh dikembalikan kepada kita. Kita juga harus menuntut Singapura dan Kepulauan Riau, karena mereka adalah Tanah Melayu,‚Äù tambahnya yang disambut tepuk tangan meriah dari para hadirin.|Dikutip dari Strait Times, Mahathir mengatakan bahwa apa yang dikenal sebagai Tanah Melayu dulunya sangat luas.|Membentang dari Tanah Genting Kra di Thailand selatan sampai ke Kepulauan Riau, dan Singapura, namun sekarang terbatas di Semenanjung Malaya.|Mahathir lantas khawatir dengan nasib Semenanjung Malaya di masa depan.|"Saya bertanya-tanya apakah Semenanjung Malaya akan menjadi milik orang lain di masa depan," katanya.|Dikutip dari Tribunnews.com, pernyataan Mahathir langsung ditanggapi oleh Deputi V Kantor Staf Presiden (KSP), Jaleswari Pramodhawardani.|Jaleswari menegaskan bahwa provinsi Kepulauan Riau merupakan bagian dari Republik Indonesia.|"Hingga detik ini, satu-satunya entitas yang memiliki kendali atas wilayah Provinsi Kepulauan Riau adalah Pemerintah Republik Indonesia," kata Jaleswari dalam keterangan tertulis, Selasa (21/6/2022).|Hal itu dibuktikan dengan adanya administrasi pemerintahan Indonesia di Kepulauan Riau yang dilakukan melalui proses demokratis.|Selain itu, pemerintah Indonesia juga menerapkan hukum nasional, pencatatan kependudukan, kemampuan penegakan hukum di provinsi tersebut.|Mengenai peryataan Mahathir, Juru Bicara Kemlu RI, Teuku Faizasyah menyebut bahwa pemerintah sedang meminta keterangan utuh dari KBRI Kuala Lumpur.|"Sedang dimintakan keterangan yang lebih utuh dari KBRI di Kuala Lumpur," kata Faizasyah saat dihubungi Tribunnews.com, pada Selasa (21/6/2022).|(Tribun-Video.com)|Artikel ini telah tayang di Tribunnews.com dengan judul Mahathir Klaim Kepulauan Riau dan Singapura Harusnya Masuk Wilayah Malaysia, Ini Respon Kemlu RI, https://www.tribunnews.com/internasional/2022/06/21/mahathir-klaim-kepulauan-riau-dan-singapura-harusnya-masuk-malaysia-ini-respon-kemlu-ri?page=all.|Host: Agung Laksono|VP: Satria Yoga

title: Introducing Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 6K G2
description: Today we introduced a new model to the Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera family, Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 6K G2. This new model includes an adjustable touchscreen screen for easier framing of shots, a larger battery for longer shooting without needing to charge or change batteries, as well as support for an optional electronic viewfinder. This new 6K model also has the latest generation 5 color science which has previously been available only in the 6K Pro model, as well as retaining the same features as the previous model including Super 35 HDR image sensor with 13 stops of dynamic range, dual native ISO of 25,600 and EF lens mount. |We also released Blackmagic Camera 7.9 Update which adds support for a new user interface which includes sliders for adjusting focus assist intensity as well as improved lens and autofocus performance for Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 4K, 6K and 6K Pro models. This update also adds support for Blackmagic Design Zoom and Focus demands to Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 6K, 6K G2 and 6K Pro models.|Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 6K G2 is available immediately from Blackmagic Design resellers worldwide for US$1,995. |Learn more at http://bmd.link/X3Va77

title: Ayodhya: Man kisses wife while bathing in river, beaten by angry mob; Video goes viral
description: A video is now going viral of a group of people beating up a man for kissing his wife in Saryu river in Uttar Pradesh's Ayodhya. An angry mob can be seen pushing and pulling out the man from the river and then ganging up on him. One man can be seen hurling abuses and asking the husband if he has no family at home. The police have launched an investigation in the incident. Netizens are now divided over the incident with a debate on Indian culture sparking off on Twitter. While many tweeted pictures of ancient statues others pointed out how kissing is not a part of Indian culture. For more details, watch this video.|#ayodhya #viralvideo #kissing #viral #saryuriver #uttarpradesh #uppolice #mobattack

title: Modi govt to give preference to 'Agniveers'; Mulls opening ONGC top post for military officers
description: Hindustan Times has learnt that the government is planning to open the top post in Oil & Natural Gas Corporation (ONGC) for military officers. Sources told HT that the government is considering formally opening chief executive positions in its blue-chip companies to senior armed force officers in ONGC. They added government is considering formally opening chief executive positions in its blue-chip companies to senior armed force officers. Remember, the top post in ONGC has been vacant since April 1, 2021. As per HT report, companies controlled by the central government may soon be asked to give preference to Agniveers, soldiers recruited under the new Agnipath scheme, on merit in various junior-level positions after they complete their tour of duty. title: AHY: Saya dan Bapak Surya Paloh Sepakat untuk Lebih Kuat dan Terbuka
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Selain Partai Demokrasi Indonesia Perjuangan magnet baru dalam peta politik Indonesia saat ini, adalah Partai Nasdem.||||Nasdem didatangi para pimpinan partai yang bicara koalisi dalam Pemilu 2024.||||Setelah pimpinan Partai Keadilan Sejahtera atau PKS, pada Rabu 22 Juni 2022, maka ada empat ketua umum partai yang sudah bertemu Ketua Umum Surya Paloh di kantornya, Nasdem Tower.||||Elite PKS dipimpin Presidennya Ahmad Syaikhu bertemu pimpinan Nasdem yang dipimpin Surya Paloh.||||Namun dalam pertemuan selama dua jam, Surya dan Syaikhu belum menyepakati koalisi.||||Nasdem dan PKS baru sepakat menyiapkan kerja sama politik dalam Pemilu serentak 2024.||||Hal tersebut juga disepakati oleh Agus Harimurti Yudhoyono yang merupakan ketua umum Partai Demokrat.||||Usai melaksanakan pertemuan tertutup tersebut, Surya Paloh dan AHY mengungkapkan bahwa kunjungan tersebut mengeratkan hubungan Partai NasDem dan Partai Demokrat. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/302087/ahy-saya-dan-bapak-surya-paloh-sepakat-untuk-lebih-kuat-dan-terbuka

title: Pyar Tune Kya Kiya | Hindi Full Movie | Fardeen Khan | Urmila Matondkar | Sonali Kulkarni
description: Pyar Tune Kya Kiya | Hindi Full Movie | Fardeen Khan | Urmila Matondkar | Sonali Kulkarni|Directed by- Rajat Mukherjee|Written by- Rajat Mukherjee|Produced by Ram Gopal Varma|Starring -Urmila Matondkar, Fardeen Khan, Sonali Kulkarni|Cinematography- Sanjay Kapoor|Edited by -Chandan Arora|Music by -Sandeep Chowta|Synopsis:-|Ria (Urmila Matondkar) is a headstrong loner angry woman and the only daughter of a rich businessman in Mumbai, Mr Jaiswal (Suresh Oberoi). Jaiswal loves his daughter but is concerned about her possessive nature. One day Ria sets out for a vacation in Goa. Jai (Fardeen Khan) is a fashion photographer, happily married to Geeta (Sonali Kulkarni). He meets Ria and takes photos of her without permission and publishes them in the magazine he works for. The magazine becomes a hit because of the pictures. The chief editor wants Ria to model for their magazine but she refuses because she is angry at Jai for publishing her pictures without asking her. Jai manages to convince her to model and she falls in love with him. She wants to talk to Jai about marriage but when she visits his home, she is shocked to meet Geeta. Shaken and distraught, Ria slips into depression.|Ria confesses her feelings to Jai, who is startled. Seeing her weeping so much, he tells her that he would have accepted her love if not married. Jai tells Geeta everything and vows to stay away from Ria. However, Ria starts to get possessive about Jai, unable to forget him. She makes a suicide attempt and calls him in the middle of the night. Jai has no choice but to save and console her. This troubles Geeta and she tells Jai to file a police complaint. Jai and Geeta mend their relationship and go out on a date but that same night, Ria breaks down and Jai consoles her again. This angers Geeta even more.|Jai attends a company party with Geeta, not knowing that Ria has also been invited. Ria now wants Jai at any cost and flirts with him in front of Geeta, who leaves fuming. At home, Jai and Geeta have a huge argument and Geeta leaves in anger. She realizes her mistake and decides to go back but Ria breaks in and starts getting intimate with Jai. Geeta enters the house and loses control on seeing them. She accidentally falls onto a glass table and hurts her head. Jai takes her to the hospital.|Ria tells Geeta that she should leave the marriage and let her and Jai live happily. Geeta explains that Jai does not love Ria as she so thinks and nothing can break their relationship. Jai decides to leave the city because of Ria's obsessive nature. Ria calls, asking to meet one last time. Jai agrees but instead goes to meet Mr Jaiswal and tells him the truth. Jai calls Geeta and hears her being attacked by someone.|It's Ria, who has become completely unstable. She attempts to kill Geeta so that she can win Jai's love. Geeta tries to escape but fails. Just as Ria is about to kill her, Jai arrives. He pleads with her to let Geeta go and he will leave Geeta to be with her. Ria, convinced, runs toward Jai but he slaps her hard, making her unconscious. Mr Jaiswal arrives and Jai tells him what Ria did.|Six months later, Geeta and Jai are happy with their life once again while Ria is housed at a mental hospital. Her father arrives at Jai's house, asking him to meet her one last time as it's her birthday and it's only Jai that can make any impact on her. Jai agrees. Upon seeing Jai, Ria loses control and shakes him until her father and the hospital crew pull her away. title: Ekonomi Jerman Terancam Resesi setelah  Rusia Balas Sanksi Barat Hentikan Ekspor Gas ke Eropa
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Operasi militer khusus Rusia ke Ukraina membuat Barat menjatuhkan sanksi terhadap Moskwa. |Termasuk Jerman yang ikut terlibat dalam pemberian sanksi tersebut. |Namun, justru ekonomi Jerman terancam mengalami resesi karena dibalas Rusia yang menghentikan ekspor energinya. |Dikutip dari Tribunnews.com, langkah kebijakan Presiden Putin yang memperketat aliran energi Rusia ke Eropa ternyata membawa dampak besar. |Rusia telah menghentikan ekspor gasnya ke sejumlah negara Uni Eropa dari Laut Baltik hingga Laut Adriatik.|Termasuk Jerman yang terkena imbasnya. |Terkini, ekonomi Jerman terancam babak belur. |Ancaman ini terjadi setelah perusahaan gas negara Rusia Gazprom memotong pasokan gasnya di pipa Nord Stream sebanyak tiga kali.|Resesi Jerman mulai tampak setelah Asosiasi Industri BDI Jerman memangkas perkiraan pertumbuhan ekonomi 2022.|Tercatat pertumbuhan ekonomi terganggu dari 3,5 persen menjadi 1,5 persen pada Selasa (21/6/2022). |‚ÄúPenghentian pengiriman gas Rusia akan membuat Jerman mengalami resesi tak terhindarkan," jelas Asosiasi industri BDI.|Diungkapkan, kini pasokan gas Rusia ke Jerman hanya bekerja dengan kapasitas 40 persen.|Padahal permintaan minyak mengalami peningkatan. |Sementara itu, Menteri Ekonomi Jerman, Robert Habeck mengaku negaranya sangat bergantung pada pasokan gas Rusia. |Kendati begitu, Jerman akan memulai beralih ke penggunaan batu bara pada akhir Juni nanti. |Hal ini sebagai langkah untuk mengurangi ketergantungan minyak dan gas Rusia. |Dengan kebijakan ini, Menteri Ekonomi optimis dapat membantu Jerman menghemat stok gasnya.|(Tribun-Video.com/ Tribunnews.com)|Video Editor: Dyah Ayu Ambarwati|Host: Bima Maulana|Artikel ini telah tayang di Tribunnews.com dengan judul Ekonomi Jerman Menuju Jurang Resesi oleh Embargo Gas Rusia, https://www.tribunnews.com/bisnis/2022/06/22/ekonomi-jerman-menuju-jurang-resesi-oleh-embargo-gas-rusia.|Penulis: Namira Yunia Lestanti|Editor: Choirul Arifin

title: Ganjar Ungkit Perintah Megawati Saat Ditanya Salam Komando Dengan Bambang Pacul
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Salam komando antara Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo dengan Bambang Wuryanto menyedot perhatian publik. ||||Pasalnya hubungan keduanya sempat dikabarkan memanas karena ketidakhadiran Ganjar di acara PDIP di Jawa Tengah. ||||Ganjar pun mengungkap keterkaitan salam komando dengan kekompakan menjalankan perintah Ketua Umum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri.||||Baca Juga Momen Ganjar dan Bambang Pacul Salam Komando Disorak Para Kader di Acara Rakernas di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301133/momen-ganjar-dan-bambang-pacul-salam-komando-disorak-para-kader-di-acara-rakernas||||"Salam komando ya kita tunjukkan ini kan rakernas nih. Kita mesti kompak dari perintah Ketum, targetnya ya kita semua mesti bekerja, sesimpel itu saja dan semua tersenyum, dan mendapatkan respons dari Indonesia, wah rakernasnya kompak, rakernasnya ini,"ujar Ganjar, Rabu (22/6/2022). ||||Ganjar pun menilai pertemanannya dengan Bambang Wuryanto seperti junior ke senior.||||"Itu biasalah, namanya juga seperti ramalan cuaca, kadang hujan kadang panas. Mas Pacul itu di UGM, temen saya, senior saya, dulu bareng di Kesekjenan bareng saya, di Badiklat bareng saya, di fraksi bareng saya, jadi biasa saja buat saya," ujarnya.||||Video Editor: Arief || ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301927/ganjar-ungkit-perintah-megawati-saat-ditanya-salam-komando-dengan-bambang-pacul

title: Partai Mana Saja Yang Akan Berkoalisi Dengan NasDem | Satu Meja The Forum (3)

title: 50 Bangkai Hewan Ternak Diduga Akibat PMK Ditemukan di Aliran Sungai Serang
description: KABUPATEN SEMARANG, KOMPAS.TV -  Warga Desa Susukan, Kabupaten Semarang Jawa Tengah menemukan sekitar 50 bangkai kambing, di aliran Sungai Serang.||||Diduga bangkai kambing dari peternakan di luar Desa Susukan, karena mempunyai tanda khusus berupa kalung yang terpasang di leher.||||Menurut saksi mata, pada Senin (20/06) malam ada sebuah truk parkir di Jembatan Sungai Serang yang diduga membuang bangkai.||||Baca Juga Kebakaran di Pondok Permata Sekumpul Martapura, Lurah Upayakan Korban dapat Bantuan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301913/kebakaran-di-pondok-permata-sekumpul-martapura-lurah-upayakan-korban-dapat-bantuan||||Dari hasil penyelidikan sementara, polisi mendapati saksi yang diminta membantu membuang puluhan bangkai kambing dengan imbalan Rp 100 ribu.||||Puluhan bangkai kambing dikirim dari Sumatera menggunakan 2 truk.||||Dari ciri fisik, dinas terkait memastikan bangkai kambing terjangkit penyakit mulut dan kuku (PMK).||||Penyidik dalri Polres Semarang menyebut total ada 97 bangkai hewan ternak yang dibuang di aliran Sungai Serang, Kabupaten Semarang.||||Baca Juga AFC Cup 2022 Zona ASEAN Mulai 24 Juni: Format & Sistem Kompetisi, Bagaimana Peluang Wakil Indonesia? di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301916/afc-cup-2022-zona-asean-mulai-24-juni-format-sistem-kompetisi-bagaimana-peluang-wakil-indonesia||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301923/50-bangkai-hewan-ternak-diduga-akibat-pmk-ditemukan-di-aliran-sungai-serang

title: BOAI Episode 9: Final Framing and Two Additional Projects!
description: In this episode of Building on an Island, Wade visits two other worksites on Block island before we head to the BOAI site. At the first home, Wade and his team are installing a slate roof. He shares why they chose slate over other roofing materials, and why slate tile roofs are called a "forever roof." On the second site, a gorgeous Queen Anne renovation, Wade discusses how they're going to restore this 160-year-old home while maintaining its historical and architectural integrity. The house had a lot of rot in the original wood, so the team replaced much of the framing and created a floor system where none originally existed. They'll also have to replace all of the windows and doors. At the Building on an Island home, Wade discusses supply chain and other issues that the team is navigating. The crew has finished miscellaneous framing in the basement, living room, and kitchen. The exterior team has been working on the balcony and the white, PVC Versatex trim, and other details, including deck boards and asphalt shingles on the roof. He even shares his roofer's method of preventing hurricane-force winds from tearing away the shingles. As the exposure limit for the Huber ZIP system approaches, Wade gets advice on how to continue without voiding the warranty so they can install shakes and a stone veneer.|Subscribe and follow my Podcast on Apple or Spotify!|Apple: https://apple.co/32AOwgU|Spotify: https://spoti.fi/3FXNg4X|Sign up for our twice-weekly newsletter:|https://buildshownetwork.com/newsletter|To sponsor a video or advertise with us visit:|https://www.buildproductions.com|Want to learn more about building? https://buildshownetwork.com/|Build Show Network on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thebuildshow/|Huge thanks to our Show sponsors Builders FirstSource, Polywall, Huber, Rockwool & Viewrail for helping to make these videos possible! title: Presiden Jokowi Membuka Kongres Nasional XXXII dan Sidang MPA XXXI PMKRI, Samarinda, 22 Juni 2022
description: *Buka Kongres Nasional ke-32 PMKRI, Presiden Pastikan IKN Pindah Sesuai Rencana*|Presiden Joko Widodo memastikan bahwa pemindahan ibu kota negara Republik Indonesia dari Jakarta ke Ibu Kota Nusantara (IKN) akan tetap dilakukan sesuai dengan rencana yang telah ditetapkan oleh pemerintah dan undang-undang. Menurut Presiden, pemindahan ibu kota negara merupakan gagasan lama dari sejumlah pemimpin Indonesia terdahulu yang belum direalisasikan hingga saat ini.|"Ini adalah sebuah mimpi lama, gagasan lama yang belum dieksekusi, dan sekarang telah kita eksekusi dan ada _back up_ undang-undangnya yaitu Undang-Undang Ibu Kota Negara," ujar Presiden dalam sambutannya saat membuka secara resmi Kongres Nasional XXXII dan Sidang Majelis Permusyawaratan Anggota XXXI Perhimpunan Mahasiswa Katolik Republik Indonesia (PMKRI) yang digelar di Samarinda Convention Hall, Kota Samarinda, pada Rabu, 22 Juni 2022.|Dalam kesempatan tersebut, Presiden memaparkan sejumlah alasan mengenai pentingnya pemindahan ibu kota negara. Salah satunya adalah pemerataan ekonomi yang ingin diwujudkan di seluruh penjuru Tanah Air dan tidak terpusat di satu pulau yang ada di Indonesia. |"Yang paling penting memang kita ingin Indonesiasentris bukan Jawasentris. Kita garis dari barat ke timur, dari utara ke selatan, ketemu di paling tengah itu yaitu Provinsi Kalimantan Timur," ungkap Presiden.|Selain itu, Presiden juga menjelaskan bahwa perpindahan ibu kota tidak hanya melakukan pemindahan secara fisik sejumlah infrastruktur yang ada di Jakarta. Menurut Presiden, perubahan pola pikir, birokrasi, dan cara kerja baru yang menggunakan teknologi akan menjadi prioritas pemerintah di IKN.|"Di sini lah akan kita mulai _future economy_, _green economy_, _future technology_, _future knowledge_ semuanya memang ingin kita lakukan di sini. Rumah sakit ya rumah sakit internasional, universitas ya universitas yang kelasnya betul-betul internasional dan kita harapkan ini juga bisa membuka yang namanya _future job_ dan _future skill_," ucap Presiden. |Presiden pun berharap IKN dapat menjadi magnet bagi talenta-talenta dalam negeri maupun luar negeri. Presiden mengatakan bahwa nantinya IKN akan memiliki desain dan fasilitas yang mendukung konsep _ten minutes city_, 70 persen area hijau, 80 persen transportasi publik ramah lingkungan, hingga penggunaan energi hijau.|"Ini desain-desain kota masa depan yang saya kira ini adalah miliknya anak-anak muda," tutur Presiden.|Turut mendampingi Presiden dalam kegiatan tersebut adalah Ketua DPR RI Puan Maharani, Menteri Sekretaris Negara Pratikno, Menteri Investasi/Kepala BKPM Bahlil Lahadalia, Menteri Pemuda dan Olahraga Zainudin Amali, Gubernur Kalimantan Timur Isran Noor, Wali Kota Samarinda Andi Harun, dan Ketua Presidium PMKRI Benidiktus Papa.|Samarinda, 22 Juni 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

title: Hundreds of thousands evacuated as floods ravage southern China - BBC News

title: The Music of Baz Luhrmann‚Äôs ELVIS
description: ‚ÄúAs far as Elvis goes, it wasn‚Äôt just about making music. It was about singing from your soul, and singing something that needed to be sung.‚Äù |Austin Butler shares his journey to embody the legend in Baz Luhrmann‚Äôs #ElvisMovie, only in theaters THIS FRIDAY. ‚ö°Ô∏è #TCB|Get tickets now: https://elvis.warnerbros.com|https://www.facebook.com/ElvisMovie |https://www.instagram.com/ElvisMovie |https://twitter.com/ElvisMovie |https://www.tiktok.com/@ElvisFilm|ELVIS is an epic, big-screen spectacle from Warner Bros. Pictures and visionary, Oscar-nominated filmmaker Baz Luhrmann that explores the life and music of Elvis Presley, starring Austin Butler and Oscar winner Tom Hanks. |A thoroughly cinematic drama, Elvis‚Äôs (Butler) story is seen through the prism of his complicated relationship with his enigmatic manager, Colonel Tom Parker (Hanks). As told by Parker, the film delves into the complex dynamic between the two spanning over 20 years, from Presley‚Äôs rise to fame to his unprecedented stardom, against the backdrop of the evolving cultural landscape and loss of innocence in America. Central to that journey is one of the significant and influential people in Elvis‚Äôs life, Priscilla Presley (Olivia DeJonge). |Starring alongside Butler and Hanks, award-winning theatre actress Helen Thomson (‚ÄúTop of the Lake: China Girl,‚Äù ‚ÄúRake‚Äù) plays Elvis‚Äôs mother, Gladys, Richard Roxburgh (‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù ‚ÄúBreath,‚Äù ‚ÄúHacksaw Ridge‚Äù) portrays Elvis‚Äôs father, Vernon, and DeJonge (‚ÄúThe Visit,‚Äù ‚ÄúStray Dolls‚Äù) plays Priscilla. Luke Bracey (‚ÄúHacksaw Ridge,‚Äù ‚ÄúPoint Break‚Äù) plays Jerry Schilling, Natasha Bassett (‚ÄúHail, Caesar!‚Äù) plays Dixie Locke, David Wenham (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings‚Äù Trilogy, ‚ÄúLion,‚Äù ‚Äú300‚Äù) plays Hank Snow, Kelvin Harrison Jr. (‚ÄúThe Trial of the Chicago 7,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe High Note‚Äù) plays B.B. King, Xavier Samuel (‚ÄúAdore,‚Äù ‚ÄúLove & Friendship,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Twilight Saga: Eclipse‚Äù) plays Scotty Moore, and Kodi Smit-McPhee (‚ÄúThe Power of the Dog‚Äù) plays Jimmie Rodgers Snow. |Also in the cast, Dacre Montgomery (‚ÄúStranger Things,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Broken Heart Gallery‚Äù) plays TV director Steve Binder, alongside Australian actors Leon Ford (‚ÄúGallipoli,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Pacific‚Äù) as Tom Diskin, Kate Mulvany (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúHunters‚Äù) as Marion Keisker, Gareth Davies (‚ÄúPeter Rabbit,‚Äù ‚ÄúHunters‚Äù) as Bones Howe, Charles Grounds (‚ÄúCrazy Rich Asians,‚Äù ‚ÄúCamp‚Äù) as Billy Smith, Josh McConville (‚ÄúFantasy Island‚Äù) as Sam Phillips, and Adam Dunn (‚ÄúHome and Away‚Äù) as Bill Black. |To play additional iconic musical artists in the film, Luhrmann cast singer/songwriter Yola as Sister Rosetta Tharpe, model Alton Mason as Little Richard, Austin, Texas native Gary Clark Jr. as Arthur Crudup, and artist Shonka Dukureh as Willie Mae ‚ÄúBig Mama‚Äù Thornton. |Oscar nominee Luhrmann (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù) directed from a screenplay by Baz Luhrmann & Sam Bromell and Baz Luhrmann & Craig Pearce and Jeremy Doner, story by Baz Luhrmann and Jeremy Doner. The film‚Äôs producers are Luhrmann, Oscar winner Catherine Martin (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù), Gail Berman, Patrick McCormick and Schuyler Weiss. Toby Emmerich, Courtenay Valenti and Kevin McCormick executive produced. |The director‚Äôs behind-the-scenes creative team includes director of photography Mandy Walker (‚ÄúMulan,‚Äù ‚ÄúAustralia‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer and costume designer Catherine Martin (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù), production designer Karen Murphy (‚ÄúA Star Is Born‚Äù), editors Matt Villa (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby,‚Äù ‚ÄúAustralia‚Äù) and Jonathan Redmond (‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù), Oscar-nominated visual effects supervisor Thomas Wood (‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù), music supervisor Anton Monsted (‚ÄúAustralia,‚Äù ‚ÄúMoulin Rouge!‚Äù) and composer Elliott Wheeler (‚ÄúThe Get Down‚Äù). |Principal photography on ‚ÄúElvis‚Äù took place in Queensland, Australia with the support of the Queensland Government, Screen Queensland, and the Australian Government‚Äôs Producer Offset program. |A Warner Bros. Pictures Presentation, A Bazmark Production, A Jackal Group Production, A Baz Luhrmann Film, ‚ÄúElvis‚Äù will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to release in theaters in North America on June 24, 2022, and internationally beginning 22 June 2022.

title: IT'S HERE! My Brand New Zenvo TSR-S in the UK | ROAD TO ZENVO Part 9

title: Obi-Wan Kenobi Ending Explained
description: HELLO THERE!|So, the Obi-Wan Kenobi series has drawn to a close and we have to say it ended in quite the fashion, with an epic lightsaber duel, some cool cameos and a return of a line we have been waiting so long for. It is all quite a satisfying conclusion, and although there are certainly some continuity quibbles and potential plot holes created by the series, it all sets up A New Hope and the classic Star Wars saga pretty nicely. |But what does this all mean? How does it play out into A New Hope? What did that final shot and line mean? And will there be a second season? These are the questions we seek to answer in this video, as will go through the final episode with a fine comb and hopefully provide the answers to any other questions you might have. We will look at the references to A New Hope, the importance of that particular showdown and the ambiguous fate of one of the show‚Äôs new characters. We will also discuss what a potential second season might look like, who could return, whether or not we will see the Skywalker twins again, who the primary antagonist could be and the possibility of the return of another familiar face. We will also use evidence from the people who worked on the show to see whether or not a second season might happen, and why there are some exciting possibilities for Obi-Wan moving forward. But before we do that, let‚Äôs go over the ending once more.|What did you make of this video? Were you a fan of the series? What did you make of the ending? Do you want a second season? If so, what would you like to see? title: Penggantian Nama Jalan oleh Pemprov DKI Ditolak Warga
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Penggantian nama jalan oleh Pemprov DKI Jakarta mendapat penolakan.||||Puluhan warga di Kebon Jeruk, Jakarta Barat menolak karena penggantian nama jalan tanpa sosialisasi.||||Baca Juga Momen Anies dan Ketua DPRD Manortor dalam Paripurna HUT DKI Jakarta ke-495 di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301633/momen-anies-dan-ketua-dprd-manortor-dalam-paripurna-hut-dki-jakarta-ke-495||||Spanduk bertuliskan penolakan pergantian nama jalan dibentangkan oleh warga Jalan Madrasah II, Sukabumi Utara, Jakarta Barat.||||Warga kecewa, kebijakan dianggap sepihak tanpa melibatkan warga dalam musyawarah.||||Warga dari 3 rukun warga menolak pergantian nama jalan. Madrasah II menjadi Syekh Abdul Karim bin Asfan.||||Selain tak ada sosialisasi, warga juga kawatir dengan masalah pengurusan administrasi domisili dan surat menyurat.||||Bahkan belum diresmikan, plang nama sudah dipasang.||||Sebelumnya, dalam menyambut hari ulang tahun DKI Jakarta ke-495, ada sekitar 22 jalan, serta 5 perkampungan yang diganti namanya.||||Pemprov DKI menyatakan, penggantian nama jalan dengan nama-nama tokoh Betawi untuk mengenang jasa para pendahulu khususnya masyarakat Betawi.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301860/penggantian-nama-jalan-oleh-pemprov-dki-ditolak-warga

title: The Office x Minions
description: Minions: The Rise of Gru | Only in Theaters July 1st. |- -|Follow #Illumination and #Minions:|https://www.instagram.com/illuminatio...|https://www.facebook.com/illuminationent|https://twitter.com/illumination|https://www.instagram.com/minions|https://www.tiktok.com/@minions|https://www.facebook.com/minions|https://twitter.com/minions|This summer, from the biggest global animated franchise in history, comes the origin story of how the world‚Äôs greatest supervillain first met his iconic Minions, forged cinema‚Äôs most despicable crew and faced off against the most unstoppable criminal force ever assembled in Minions: The Rise of Gru.| |Long before he becomes the master of evil, Gru (Oscar¬Æ nominee Steve Carell) is just a 12-year-old boy in 1970s suburbia, plotting to take over the world from his basement. |It‚Äôs not going particularly well. When Gru crosses paths with the Minions, including Kevin, Stuart, Bob, and Otto‚Äîa new Minion sporting braces and a desperate need to please‚Äîthis unexpected family joins forces. Together, they build their first lair, design their first weapons, and strive to execute their first missions.| |When the infamous supervillain supergroup, the Vicious 6, oust their leader‚Äîlegendary martial arts fighter Wild Knuckles (Oscar¬Æ winner Alan Arkin)‚Äî Gru, their most devoted fanboy, interviews to become their newest member. The Vicious 6 is not impressed by the diminutive, wannabe villain, but then Gru outsmarts (and enrages) them, and he suddenly finds himself the mortal enemy of the apex of evil. With Gru on the run, the Minions attempt to master the art of kung fu to help save him, and Gru discovers that even bad guys need a little help from their friends. | |Featuring more spectacular action than any film in Illumination history and packed with the franchise‚Äôs signature subversive humor, Minions: The Rise of Gru stars a thrilling new cast, including, the Vicious 6: Taraji P. Henson as cool and confident leader Belle Bottom, whose chain belt doubles as a lethal disco-ball mace; Jean-Claude Van Damme as the nihilistic Jean Clawed, who‚Äôs armed (literally) with a giant robotic claw; Lucy Lawless as Nunchuck, whose traditional nun‚Äôs habit hides her deadly nun-chucks; Dolph Lundgren as Swedish roller-skate champion Svengeance, who dispenses his enemies with spin kicks from his spiked skates; and Danny Trejo as Stronghold, whose giant iron hands are both a menace to others and a burden to him. | |The film also stars Russell Brand as Young Dr. Nefario, an aspiring mad scientist, Michelle Yeoh as Master Chow, an acupuncturist with mad kung fu skills, and Oscar¬Æ winner Julie Andrews as Gru‚Äôs maddeningly self-absorbed mom.| |Steered by the franchise‚Äôs original creators, Minions: The Rise of Gru is produced by visionary Illumination founder and CEO Chris Meledandri and his longtime collaborators Janet Healy and Chris Renaud. The film is directed by returning franchise filmmaker Kyle Balda (Despicable Me 3, Minions), co-directed by Brad Ableson (The Simpsons) and Jonathan del Val (The Secret Life of Pets films), and features the iconic voice of Pierre Coffin as the Minions and a killer ‚Äô70s soundtrack courtesy of legendary Grammy-winning music producer Jack Antonoff.

Valenti.||||Based on the best-selling book series by Bernard Waber, Lyle, Lyle, Crocodile stars Constance Wu, Scoot McNairy, Javier Bardem, Winslow Fegley, Brett Gelman. title: Is Sri Lanka a victim of Chinese 'debt traps'? - BBC Newsnight
description: Sri Lanka's economic crisis continues to run out of control and the country is requesting an emergency bailout from the International Monetary Fund. |However, the major debts the country has racked up in borrowing from China are standing in the way of a bailout being agreed. |Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|Chinese money has flooded into many developing countries over the past few years but some claim that these loans are designed as 'debt traps'.|It's claimed that if a country can't repay then China is entitled to seize critical infrastructure such as ports and thereby strengthen it's global influence. |Others suggest that China is not in fact exploiting developing nations but their investment may facilitate more local level corruption. |Newsnight's economics editor Ben Chu went to Sri Lanka to investigate the impact of Chinese money and what implications this may have for the global cost of living crisis. |The film was produced by Scarlett Barter and filmed/ edited by Jack Garland. Production support was provided by Zaufaran Mohamed.|Newsnight is the BBC's flagship news and current affairs TV programme - with analysis, debate, exclusives, and robust interviews. |Website: https://www.bbc.co.uk/newsnight |Twitter: https://twitter.com/BBCNewsnight |Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewsnight.|#BBCNews

title: [Full] Pernyataan Lengkap Surya Paloh dan Presiden PKS di DPP Nasdem
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden PKS Ahmad Syaikhu bertandang ke kantor DPP Partai Nasdem di Jakarta pada 22 Juni 2022.||||Presiden PKS Ahmad Syaikhu bertemu dengan Ketum Partai Nasdem Surya Paloh.||||Usai pertemuan, Surya Paloh mengatakan belum ada satu hal yang cukup serius menjadi pembahasan keduanya.||||Baca Juga Sinyal Koalisi Nasdem-PKS Mulai Kencang, Surya Paloh Sebut Sudah Ada Modal Awal untuk Bersama di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301725/sinyal-koalisi-nasdem-pks-mulai-kencang-surya-paloh-sebut-sudah-ada-modal-awal-untuk-bersama||||"Bagi kami berdua belum ada satu hal yang cukup serius menjadi pembahasan di antara kami, tetapi telah mendapatkan sesuatu yang dimaknai," kata Surya pada wartawan.
